    """
    """
    Improved version of `equation_v0` that models nonlinear harmonic oscillator acceleration.
    
    Acceleration y = params[0] + params[1]*time + params[2]*position + params[3]*position^3 + params[4]*velocity
    
    Parameters:
    - x0: time
    - x1: position at time t
    - x2: velocity at time t
    - params: array of parameters
    
    Returns:
